text.tspan: This diagram shows the relationship between the Linux kernel developers for the 2.6.18 kernel release as
described by the "Signed-off-by:" and "Acked-by:" paths that are used to develop and review all Linux kernel changes.
Created by Greg Kroah-Hartman as part of a presentation for the 2007 Linux Symposium.
Released under the Creative Commons Attribution-Noncommercial 3.0 License
Colors refer to the first letter of the developer's name.
